caption.p: The cytotoxic effect of (PJ) four solvent fractions on HeLa cells which were treated with different concentrations of (a) acetone, (b) hexane, (c) methanol, and (d) water fractions incubated for 24 h. Results were depicted as relative quantities (RQs) compared to the control (with only media). ∗ P < 0.0001 and # P < 0.01. Error bars represent ±SD.
